    <title>ThruZero Commons - Domain File System</title>
  </properties>
  <body>
    <section name="Overview">
      <p>
        This module contains File System specific implementations of the domain layer.
      </p>

      <subsection name="DAOs">
        <ul>
          <li>
            <b><a href="apidocs/com/thruzero/domain/dsc/dao/DscPreferenceDAO.html">DscPreferenceDAO</a></b>:
            An implementation of PreferenceDAO that uses the file system as storage.
          </li>

          <li>
            <b><a href="apidocs/com/thruzero/domain/dsc/dao/DscSettingDAO.html">DscSettingDAO</a></b>:
            An implementation of SettingDAO that uses the file system as storage.
          </li>

          <li>
            <b><a href="apidocs/com/thruzero/domain/dsc/dao/DscTextEnvelopeDAO.html">DscTextEnvelopeDAO</a></b>:
            An implementation of TextEnvelopeDAO that uses the file system as storage.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>

      <subsection name="Services">
        <ul>
          <li>
            <b><a href="apidocs/com/thruzero/domain/dsc/service/DscInfoNodeService.html">DscInfoNodeService</a></b>:
            An InfoNodeService implemented explicitly to use the file system as storage (using DscTextEnvelopeDAO).
          </li>

        </ul>
      </subsection>
    </section>

